* Fix typo on ${FCV} in makefile.in
* Try ${MV} w*.so once again.

For non-standard locations (Libs & Headers): 

Example:
./configure LDFLAGS='-L/home/user/test/lib' CPPFLAGS='-I/home/user/test/lib'

For Python3 and / or f2py:

Example:
./configure --with-python3='/usr/local/bin/python3' --with-f2py='/opt/bin/f2py'


